Hello guys,&lt;BR&gt;

Special event ! To celebrate dedicated servers with 1Gbit/s (shared) bandwidth on IKOULA, this option is free on any 1220 or 1230 dedicated server ordered before the 31/05.&lt;BR&gt;

As always feel free to ask if you have any question.&lt;BR&gt;

**Specifications**&lt;BR&gt;
-Xeon E3 1220v5 3.4 GHz processor or Xeon E3 1230v5 3.4 GHz processor&lt;BR&gt;
-8 GB Ram&lt;BR&gt;
-1 TB Sata Hd&lt;BR&gt;
-1 Gbps (shared - unmetered)&lt;BR&gt;
-Location : France&lt;BR&gt;

**Choice of OS**&lt;BR&gt;
-VMware ESXi (pré-installation)&lt;BR&gt;
-CentOS 7 64 bits&lt;BR&gt;
-Debian 8 64 bits&lt;BR&gt;
-Debian 9 64 bits&lt;BR&gt;
-Ubuntu 16.04 64 bits&lt;BR&gt; 

**Price**&lt;BR&gt;
-Price : 34.5$ excl VAT/month for 1220 and 46$ excl VAT/month for 1230&lt;BR&gt;
-Promo 1 : The 1Gbps option is automaticaly selected when you order the server. 
-Promo 2 : You can apply a discount of -50% off on your first subscription period (1 or 3 months, payable upfront) if you use the code SERV50 at the end of the order.&lt;BR&gt;

**Accepted methods of payments**&lt;BR&gt;
-Paypal&lt;BR&gt;
-Credit cards&lt;BR&gt;
-Bank tranfer&lt;BR&gt;

**Order link**&lt;BR&gt;
https://ikou.la/47&lt;BR&gt;

**Server administration**&lt;BR&gt;
-Root&lt;BR&gt;
-Reboot&lt;BR&gt;
-Reset&lt;BR&gt;
-Customized reverse DNS&lt;BR&gt;
-Customized secondary DNS&lt;BR&gt;
-MX rescue&lt;BR&gt;
-Rescue system tools are available on https://extranet.ikoula.com&lt;BR&gt;

**IP / Network**&lt;BR&gt;
-Extra IPv4 is charged 2.80$ / Month (limited to five).&lt;BR&gt;
-Ipv6 available but not configured by default.&lt;BR&gt;
-You can test our network at http://lg.ikoula.com/&lt;BR&gt;
-DRAC / KVMoIP Not incluted, a KVM can be rent for 24h.&lt;BR&gt;

**Info**&lt;BR&gt;
Operating since 1998 and we own two datacenters. More info &lt;a href="https://www.ikoula.com/en/ikoula-datacenter-france"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;BR&gt;
